1
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:08,959
[Previously]
They want to pin the sins of that day

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,679
along with the risk of exterminating the clan

3
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:12,439
all on you.

4
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:14,160
Huan Dong.

5
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:15,320
Though this matter is small,

6
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:17,839
it is my first act for the Huan family.

7
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:19,239
It must be swift and decisive.

8
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:20,759
An eighth-grade quasi-divine pill...

9
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:23,359
should be enough to propel me straight into mid-Nascent Soul.

10
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:25,039
This scheme is treacherous,

11
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,439
yet I have no choice but to enter it.

12
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:27,919
That person's cultivation...

13
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:29,200
is formidable.

14
00:00:29,280 --> 00:00:30,079
If he joins the fray,

15
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,559
he will surely help Ran Yunxing

16
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:32,840
survive this calamity.

17
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:34,279
The Sun family has given the order:

18
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,719
the auction of this item

19
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:36,999
must not be interfered with.

20
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:38,839
If no fellow Daoist bids again,

21
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,959
this eighth-grade spiritual pill will be withdrawn.

22
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:42,080
I bid...

23
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,759
one immortal jade.

24
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,600
One immortal jade.

25
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:57,400
Has he lost his mind?

26
00:00:57,720 --> 00:00:58,720
Who is this guy?

27
00:00:58,920 --> 00:00:59,999
He's openly humiliating Baohe Tower!

28
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,559
He actually made a bid.

29
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,479
But that price...

30
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:04,639
Accept it.

31
00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:06,199
Baohe Tower's reputation will be ruined.

32
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:08,559
It would tell everyone there's fraud involved.

33
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:10,520
Don't accept it.

34
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:13,199
The ancestor strictly ordered that this item must be sold.

35
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,199
Brother Xu...

36
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,439
Brilliant.

37
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:18,440
I’m impressed.

38
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,879
Since...

39
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,839
only this fellow Daoist has bid,

40
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,039
sold!

41
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:28,879
The eighth-grade spiritual pill

42
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:30,039
for one immortal jade

43
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,159
now belongs

44
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,679
to this fellow Daoist.

45
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,439
It’s sold.

46
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,719
Why did Baohe Tower accept it?

47
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,159
That was an eighth-grade quasi-divine pill!

48
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,159
Baohe Tower is treating this like a joke.

49
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,759
Fellow Daoist Sun, if there’s nothing else,

50
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,679
I shall take my leave.

51
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:46,999
Wang.

52
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:02,959
What is it?

53
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,239
Inside here

54
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:16,239
are the fifty thousand immortal jades I’ve saved over the years.

55
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,879
There are also some of my lifelong insights

56
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,679
on pill refinement and artifact crafting.

57
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:26,999
I originally thought that one day

58
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,679
I might find an opportunity

59
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:32,399
to restore a portion of my cultivation.

60
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,599
But now… they’re of no use to me.

61
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,199
I’ll give them to you.

62
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,279
Life and death.

63
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,479
Strength and weakness.

64
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,839
Kindness and resentment.

65
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,879
Cause and effect.

66
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:51,880
I greet my master.

67
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,280
Karma...

68
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,639
After comprehending the intent of the cycle of life and death,

69
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,879
is this what follows?

70
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,279
This is the true origin of life and death.

71
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,999
The cause of yesterday

72
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,399
becomes the effect of today.

73
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,039
Sun Tai came here because of me

74
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,759
and found peace because of me.

75
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,000
This...

76
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,959
is karma.

77
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,159
Nearly three hundred thousand immortal jades.

78
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,199
That should be just enough to break through in cultivation.

79
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,040
Array...

80
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,959
activate!

81
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,440
Shatter!

82
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:46,679
Such terrifying power...

83
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,479
Is this a warning to us?

84
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,079
My immortal energy is sufficient.

85
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:33,039
All that remains is to comprehend the intent.

86
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,359
Then it will come naturally.

87
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,079
I will step into mid-Nascent Soul.

88
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:41,759
Since you insist on dragging me into this affair,

89
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,359
you’d better show enough sincerity.

90
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,639
My actions just now

91
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,719
must have made those three people

92
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,719
realize what’s at stake.

93
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,199
A true breakthrough...

94
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,559
One test will tell.

95
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:00,879
Immortal guard,

96
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,360
go.

97
00:06:02,384 --> 00:06:24,484
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

98
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,559
If he wanted to kill me,

99
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,239
that palm strike earlier

100
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,879
would have already destroyed my body and soul.

101
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,759
Just what is this person’s cultivation level?

102
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,559
The Huan family has truly arrived.

103
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:46,919
I am Huan Dong,
second-grade clan guard of the Huan family
from the Thousand Illusions Main Star.

104
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:47,920
Huan Dong.

105
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,919
Nascent Soul cultivators of Ran Cloud Star,

106
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:52,759
come forth and pay your respects at once.

107
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:05,959
Scram.

108
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,000
Scram!

109
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,480
Courting death!

110
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,520
Who are you?

111
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,959
How dare you obstruct the Huan family?

112
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,199
My name...

113
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,799
You are not worthy of knowing it.

114
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,439
Silent Extinction.

115
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,080
Condense!

116
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:48,680
What kind of lightning is this?

117
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:51,679
This person’s cultivation is definitely
not mid-stage Nascent Soul!

118
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:53,680
Run!

119
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,439
I must escape.

120
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,440
Report back to the young miss!

121
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,519
With your meager strength,

122
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,039
you dare oppose my Huan family?

123
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,400
If you don’t release me at once,

124
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,119
you will all die without question.

125
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:28,719
The Huan family’s retaliation is already inevitable.

126
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:30,359
We cannot possibly resist them.

127
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:32,959
Fortunately, Xu Mu is here today.

128
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:35,840
Fellow Daoist Huan,

129
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:39,199
May I ask what business brings you
to our Ran Cloud Star?

130
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:40,279
Business?

131
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:40,759
Business?

132
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,239
Ran family Patriarch,

133
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:43,879
you should know exactly why.

134
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,439
Four years ago,
my Huan family’s people

135
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,079
were indeed killed by you.

136
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,639
Ran Xuefeng,

137
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,599
Sun Xi,

138
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,199
Zhao Chuanwen.

139
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:54,719
Zhao Chuanwen!

140
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:55,999
The bloodlines of your three families

141
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,120
have reached their end.

142
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,320
Fellow Daoist Xu,

143
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,399
This man...

144
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:01,559
Why don’t you hand him over to us?

145
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,760
Fellow Daoist Xu,

146
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:06,279
Our Huan family’s ancestor has already returned.

147
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:07,839
How dare you act this way?

148
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,599
Could it be that with your mere Nascent Soul cultivation,

149
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,439
you actually believe you can oppose our ancestor?

150
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,399
Your Huan family ancestor...

151
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:15,960
What is his cultivation?

152
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:19,519
The ancestor has stepped into the second major realm of cultivation.

153
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:22,359
Thousands of years ago,
he had already reached the Yin Void Yang Solid stage.

154
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,079
This person is yours.

155
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,679
It has nothing to do with me.

156
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,159
I still have important matters to attend to.

157
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,719
I’ll take my leave first.

158
00:14:46,560 --> 00:14:47,999
I am a personal guard of Young Miss Huan Mei.

159
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,239
My young miss

160
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,479
is the closed-door disciple that the ancestor took in
when he traveled to the Alliance.

161
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:52,800
If you dare touch me,

162
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,799
Young Miss Huan Mei will never let you go.

163
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,399
Huan Mei...

164
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,279
What was this person’s original name?

165
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:00,640
Spare me,

166
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,760
and I’ll tell you.

167
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,119
Soul Search!

168
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:11,039
Liu Mei.

169
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:15,439
This girl has truly obtained a great fortune.

170
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:18,479
Coming all the way to the Luotian Star Domain...

171
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:24,880
Fellow Daoist Xu,

172
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:26,120
Since Huan Dong is dead,

173
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:28,039
the Huan family will definitely investigate.

174
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:29,040
Within three months,

175
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,279
I will return.

176
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:41,199
Clan guard Huan Dong’s soul lamp has been extinguished.

177
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,599
Confirmed fallen.

178
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,639
Location of death:

179
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,719
Ran Cloud Star.

180
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,199
Requesting the ancestor to issue orders.

181
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,439
Dispatch troops to Ran Cloud Star.

182
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:55,359
Raze its stars to the ground.

183
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,479
Destroy its Dao lineage.

184
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:57,919
Raze its stars to the ground.

185
00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:59,239
Destroy its Dao lineage.

186
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,639
Ran Cloud Star

187
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,279
is but a tiny speck of land.

188
00:16:07,040 --> 00:16:08,279
Destroying it

189
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:10,479
would be as easy as flipping my hand.

190
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,199
Huan Dong

191
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,639
belongs to Huan Mei.

192
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,120
This grudge

193
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:20,159
shall be avenged by her personally.

194
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:22,400
Understood.

195
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:24,039
The ancestor is wise.

196
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:27,119
However, Young Miss Huan Mei’s
Blood Exchange Grand Technique has not yet...

197
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,519
Then begin it ahead of schedule.

198
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:31,759
Once the Blood Exchange Grand Technique is complete,

199
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,319
Huan Mei

200
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:35,079
will personally handle this matter.

201
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:38,479
We shall respectfully obey the ancestor’s decree.

202
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,440
Pass down my orders.

203
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,759
Effective immediately,

204
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:44,799
seal off all star passageways
leading to and from Ran Cloud Star.

205
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:46,719
Deploy the Star-Locking Grand Array.

206
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:47,679
No one is allowed in.

207
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:49,079
No one is allowed out.

208
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,639
Not even a single ant

209
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:53,319
is permitted to escape from me.

210
00:17:03,865 --> 00:17:05,865
[Cloud-Hidden Star]

211
